name: Harley Quinn - Margot Robbie - Character LORA
description:
Trained on SDv1-5-pruned with 66 pictures.
Best result with weight between : 0.8-1.

Prompt activator : harleyquinn

Other prompts : twintails, multicolored hair, cosplay, fishnet pantyhose, gloves, jacket, jewelry, lipstick, makeup, shorts, spiked bracelet, torn clothes, baseball bat

A lot of pictures had smeared lipstick (like 30-40). The model handles it good. It looks like smeared lipstick when it appears.

Commissioned on fiverr

Reviews are really appreciated, i love to see the community use my work, that's why I share it.
If you like my work, you can tip me here.

Got a specific request ? I'm open for commission on my fiverr gig *! If you provide enough data, OCs are accepted

*Any paid request will not be presented on this page, unless you give me permission to.
